fields.title: Gordan Ramsey Makes Scrambled Eggs
fields.content: Gordon Ramsay may be famous for creating beautiful and luxurious meals, but the one dish the highly decorated Michelin-starred chef and TV personality says he uses to judge a new cook is rather simple: scrambled eggs.

fields.title: Happy birthday Enya, one of the world's top-earning female artists
fields.content: The 'Only Time' and 'Orinoco Flow' singer was born as Eithne Pádraigín Ní Bhraonáin in Gweedore, County Donegal, on May 17, 1961.
